  "text": "The fault-detection effectiveness is a major metric for evaluating a testing method. Normally, the more faults a testing method can detect, the more effective it is. In this study, we evaluate the fault-detection effectiveness of the scenario-oriented approach via mutation analysis [CITATION_1] . RQ3: Is the proposed approach better than random testing?",
